[[[description]]]
Checks whether the given [zval](https://phpinternals.net/docs/zval) has a `null` value (see this [`IS_NULL`](https://phpinternals.net/docs/is_null) type).

[[[additional_information]]]
This macro also has a counterpart macro, `Z_ISNULL_P`, that accepts a pointer to a zval instead.
